{"tid":1691304,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[勝算在握] 和理非想快d贏就入黎睇","createTime":"2019-11-03T15:15:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T16:54:06.000Z","uid":329466,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d8af5835683ca61137a89bd749ad31a690361591","tid":1691304,"uid":329466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:15:27.000Z","msg":"由林奠條仆街係咁叫<span style=\"color: red;\">和理非割席</span>去到依家<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">亂鳩咁拉</span></span>就知我地贏梗，但又知叫你罷工係無可能<br />\n<br />\n要加快贏，我地可以有<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">3</span></span>方面入手<br />\n<br />\n1. <span style=\"color: red;\">破釜沉舟</span> - 唔好再俾區選同埋人權法限死自己。 區選唔多講，港共要玩野佢隨時都可以取消，用呢個黎限死自己絕對係on9.另外，人權法，美國其實由1984年已經賣左我地，就算通唔通過都好，都唔應該由佢主導左我地行為<br />\n<br />\n2. <span style=\"color: red;\">背水一戰</span> - 要接受將來既升級. eg.藍罷食變成紅裝飾/裝修。 對家已經不斷升級，你仲要原地踏步?<br />\n<br />\n3.<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">學識奉獻</span></span> <br />\n- 頭先講左，叫和理非罷工(包括我)基本上難過共產黨倒台。既然係咁，就要學識奉獻。每個月可唔可以係你<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">人工/番多份兼職</span></span>捐十分一出黎? 捐去邊隨你。 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">美國打贏二次大戰都要市民買子彈喇，你唔係以為出一出黎就夠下話?</span></span>。 真係經濟緊手既，咪15分之一，20分之一囉。都係幾千蚊數姐，咪食少幾餐去小次旅行。另外，平時番工個陣，可唔帶定多件衫同遮係身? 唔係叫你做神獸，係俾神獸事後著番。<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n<br />\n記住，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">革命</span></span>你一定要預左會流血，會有傷亡。香港地，有層樓，要罷工真係好難，但我相信以上三點，絕對大家做到。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一齊還拖，D day is coming</span></span>"},{"pid":"e3c81d8019c2a41dc6ab51fa79c53cd2d7bf40b1","tid":1691304,"uid":329466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:15:42.000Z","msg":"p牌無人權 照推"},{"pid":"976d04e113166f3a0603ef77137324ca675f1404","tid":1691304,"uid":329466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:15:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />D day is coming"},{"pid":"469788bab0102d19344039b4de6af75528060a06","tid":1691304,"uid":177600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:17:28.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"e9d12ab39376c2cea17eeb0b3a0809f8443b10b2","tid":1691304,"uid":297569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:18:06.000Z","msg":"p牌身同感受<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n［警世］唔好咁易受風向影響<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1691168\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1691168</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0677183737183837b1763d3f5f34f65ac8fafa1e","tid":1691304,"uid":329466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:18:50.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"11c3fdd8642ce47638fb8a190f4969f0453f2b51","tid":1691304,"uid":154433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:19:59.000Z","msg":"贊成有經濟能力捐出部分人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n宜家班細路同你地爭取民主，唔通大家想坐享其成？"},{"pid":"a857e78ac2602a2f65f8cf386c4debabf4f179c7","tid":1691304,"uid":52283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:21:39.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"93ac7e7efa99a701693186ec549c4df80aa66c15","tid":1691304,"uid":329466,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"11c3fdd8642ce47638fb8a190f4969f0453f2b51","tid":1691304,"uid":154433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:19:59.000Z","msg":"贊成有經濟能力捐出部分人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n宜家班細路同你地爭取民主，唔通大家想坐享其成？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:21:58.000Z","msg":"其實都係1000至幾千既野 平常生活絕對慳到出黎 細路唔係要大家係fb嬲嬲嬲 都知大家有家室走唔到上黎 但銀彈點都多多小小有"},{"pid":"de4c3bf5712b68de21e9008355dfe6c6933af4e1","tid":1691304,"uid":329466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:23:42.000Z","msg":"#whip#甴近平甴近平"},{"pid":"09737074dfd588c89625359b62ba1b716666730a","tid":1691304,"uid":329466